descriptionHtml:
Fistiq  is  Nord  Ranger Follower
Her skills are One-Handed weapons ,  Archery ,Light Armor and Stealth.
She is compatible with any body/face textures you use. 
Marriable.UFO ,EFF  compatible.

Location:
Fistiq  can be found at the Temple of Mara in Riften.

Required: ApachiiSkyHair_v_1_5_Full 
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168
Optional:
